        <updateDate>2008-06-19T16:21:50Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Senior Citizenship Act of 2008 - Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to exempt certain older persons from the naturalization U.S. history-government and English language requirements and permit certain other older persons to take such history-government examination in a language other than English.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
